# Project Structure

The Ecosia iOS browser is based on Firefox iOS with customizations. The project is organized as follows:

- `firefox-ios/` - Main iOS project directory
  - `Client/` - Main application code (Firefox base)
  - `Ecosia/` - Ecosia-specific framework and customizations
  - `EcosiaTests/` - Test suite for Ecosia functionality
  - `Shared/` - Shared utilities between iOS and other platforms
  - `Storage/`, `Sync/`, `Account/` - Core Firefox functionality

## Code Organization

- UI components should be placed in dedicated UI folders
- Business logic belongs in Core/Analytics folders
- Extensions and helpers should be in dedicated folders
